text: Jukka Koskilahti (born 23 May 1954 in Turku, Finland) is a Finnish former ice hockey player. He also played in Sweden for club teams like HV 71 (1979-1980) and Modo AIK (1980-1982). == References == Category:1954 births Category:Finnish ice hockey left wingers Category:Ice hockey people from Turku Category:Living people
title: Jukka Koskilahti
